      <title>人工智能驱动的电力热潮将推动美国顶级电网需求增长 38%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/ai-driven-power-boom-will-drive-demand-38-higher-on-top-us-grid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人工智能的热潮，美国最大电网的电力需求将快速增长，相当于未来十年安装两个新英格兰网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/ai-driven-power-boom-will-drive-demand-38-higher-on-top-us-grid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 23:38:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶周末有降雨，火灾区附近可能出现山体滑坡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/la-risks-landslides-near-fire-zones-with-weekend-rain-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南加州即将迎来春季以来的首场大雨，而洛杉矶正准备应对近期野火附近可能发生的山体滑坡和危险的径流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/la-risks-landslides-near-fire-zones-with-weekend-rain-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 23:27:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府寻求更多飞机用于大规模驱逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-administration-seeking-more-aircraft-for-mass-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫副办公厅主任史蒂芬·米勒周五表示，特朗普政府正在从六个来源确保足够的飞机，以加快将移民驱逐出美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-administration-seeking-more-aircraft-for-mass-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 23:17:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的司法部叫停法学院学生无薪暑期实习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-s-doj-halts-unpaid-summer-internships-for-law-students</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据多位知情人士透露，美国司法部已撤回了志愿法律实习计划的邀请，并告知法学院学生将不再拥有暑期职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-s-doj-halts-unpaid-summer-internships-for-law-students</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 23:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
