      <title>两名议员被驱逐，斯洛伐克联盟多数席位面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/slovak-coalition-s-majority-faces-test-as-two-lawmakers-expelled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克第二大执政党开除了两名要求担任政府职务的议员，这引发了人们对执政联盟是否仍控制议会多数席位的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/slovak-coalition-s-majority-faces-test-as-two-lawmakers-expelled</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 22:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将审理税收资助宗教学校案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/supreme-court-to-consider-bid-to-allow-religious-charter-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院接受了一场新的重大政教对决，同意考虑拥有公立特许学校的州是否根据宪法要求批准和资助宗教机构作为纳税人支持计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/supreme-court-to-consider-bid-to-allow-religious-charter-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥与中国外长王毅通话强调“美国优先”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/marco-rubio-stresses-america-first-in-call-with-china-s-wang-yi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期对华鹰派的美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥周五在与中国外交部长王毅的首次正式通话中表达了对北京对台湾采取胁迫行为以及在南海采取侵略行为的担忧，这一迹象表明中美关系可能陷入动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/marco-rubio-stresses-america-first-in-call-with-china-s-wang-yi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在视察火灾现场前受到加州州长纽瑟姆的欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-says-he-ll-seek-more-funding-for-north-carolina-floods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统抵达洛杉矶时受到加州州长加文·纽瑟姆的欢迎，他亲眼目睹了持续大规模的山火造成的破坏，山火烧毁了整个街区并造成了数十亿美元的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-says-he-ll-seek-more-funding-for-north-carolina-floods</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:32:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队就银行监管机构展开辩论，而乔普拉仍留在消费者金融保护局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-team-debates-bank-watchdog-picks-as-chopra-remains-at-cfpb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登时代任命的两位银行监管机构负责人本周继续上班，一些唐纳德·特朗普的支持者开始质疑，为什么总统没有提名人来领导这些机构，或者至少解雇现任负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-team-debates-bank-watchdog-picks-as-chopra-remains-at-cfpb</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
